title: r/Askreddit What's The Biggest Bullet You Dodged
description: r/Askreddit 2020 has been an absolutely crazy year, but sometimes it's good to remember that things could always be worse... much worse. Listen to these stories of people who have dodged catastrophic mistakes. We have one story from a hitchhiker who was almost abducted, and a kid who discovers a live WWII munitions round in his grandmother's basement. If you like this video, be sure to subscribe for more daily Reddit content!
